      "id": "mem-project_db_schema-how-to-add-a-user-to-a-workspa",
      "content": "```sql\n-- workspace_members has role; channel_members does NOT\nINSERT INTO public.workspace_members (workspace_id, user_id, role)\nVALUES ('<ws_id>', '<user_id>', 'member') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;\n\nINSERT INTO public.channel_members (channel_id, user_id)\nSELECT c.id, '<user_id>'\nFROM public.channels c\nWHERE c.workspace_id = '<ws_id>'\nON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;\n```",
